Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:05.49,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,派遣到職業現場去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.54,0:00:07.95,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,並且要留下可見實績的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:09.04,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,實地研修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:13.79,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個試煉正進入白熱化階段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:17.01,shiki Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs105\pos(1023,621)}試開業 最後一日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.09,0:00:15.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:17.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(807,1011)}suer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:17.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,出水的時機不對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:19.76,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢等不要著急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,細心地想像蔬菜出水的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:24.22,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.51,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好好記住這個表面的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:27.18,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.98,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,法國菜真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:34.56,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和傳統的日本料理的思考方式完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:35.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:37.98,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,日本料理一般傾向於不加工食材
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:40.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,儘可能地讓原材料保持原汁原味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:44.37,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,相反法國菜會花費大量的時間和功夫加工食材
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:48.20,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,光是製作高湯就很費時了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:51.33,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,與日本料理的昆布高湯是完全不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:52.21,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:56.25,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,阿貝爾還真是悉心教導呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:00:58.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你連法國菜的基礎都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:00.01,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,知不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:01.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:04.26,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要製作的魚料理配方都記清楚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:06.10,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:09.18,shokeki_huamian,NTP,0,0,0,800;446,{\frz3.522\move(1200,669,975,666)}poêler
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.85,0:01:09.18,shokeki_huamian,NTP,0,0,0,976;440,{\frz2.431\move(1464,660,1236,660)}油煎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:09.27,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:10.35,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,準備的怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.94,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的比賽想好做什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.69,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上是決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:17.61,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是差點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:19.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:22.11,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是最後一天也不要疏忽大意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.57,0:01:23.11,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:24.36,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,1002)}oui chef
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:24.36,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 大廚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.28,0:01:28.33,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我一定會做出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:31.37,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我才能創造出的「必殺料理」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,----------------------OP------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:05.97,shiki Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,954)\fad(500,200)}威風堂堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.23,0:03:07.26,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮大廚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:09.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,東京SHINO's的試開業取得巨大成功呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.35,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有開第三家店的打算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.16,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太著急了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我首要的目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:20.18,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,把東京SHINO's打造成和巴黎店齊名的餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:22.55,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:23.72,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是三號桌 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:25.85,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平 這邊也要麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:28.30,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,六號桌的客人來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.94,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先去準備五號桌的魚料理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.21,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝光顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:36.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了 試開業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.52,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到最後一天這麼快就關門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有關門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.91,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我還邀請了最後一組包場的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:52.50,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.48,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.70,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:57.75,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 因為要進行實地研修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.26,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,居然讓幸平君來幫忙卻無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.60,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不叫我來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.83,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是還有自己的店嗎 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.93,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.39,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平創真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:13.10,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 你的實習場所在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,上次見面是合宿研修的時候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.03,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,秋季選拔賽辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:20.11,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,過獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:25.12,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沙佩爾老師就是在我們當學生的時候上任的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.62,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,久疏問候了 沙佩爾老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.62,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你的雙眼很迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.33,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:33.85,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你從以前開始就是一位充滿活力的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.92,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然那時候總是讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:38.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在看起來應該沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:40.22,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你感到十分的自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:41.97,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續往上攀登吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:43.34,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.68,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請到裡面去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:48.21,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是東京SHINO's的主廚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.18,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.08,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誰是夫人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:56.19,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別逗我了 小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.69,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮前輩的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:58.73,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.65,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是隨便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:03.15,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幾年不回家一趟突然間就到東京這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:03.78,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.27,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有在反省啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:06.62,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這不是邀請你過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.54,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,來這種地方真不習慣 渾身難受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.25,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別生氣啦 放輕鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:12.95,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那是日語對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:15.71,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 四宮前輩像換了個人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.47,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.19,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 四宮前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.47,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,以前就想問了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.69,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮前輩為什麼選擇了法國料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.08,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那是為了慶祝我上小學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.62,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是唯一一次父母帶著我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.71,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去家鄉當地的一家法國餐廳進餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.38,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上唯一的一件體面衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:01.71,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在家不停地練習使用刀叉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:05.34,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,現在看來那算不上一家很出色的餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:08.18,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,小次郎 好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:13.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽也是第一次吃到這麼好吃的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.93,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,法國菜真厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.06,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我當上了法國料理廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.66,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就能一直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.78,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為媽媽帶來笑容了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:32.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我有必須告訴你的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.04,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:34.83,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.29,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是時候準備甜品了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:41.31,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,關於第一天做的洛林派
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在歐美人眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.76,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,牛蒡只不過是樹根一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:52.01,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對於日本人會吃這樣的東西感到很震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:54.97,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,包括其他的根菜類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:57.06,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,比如蘿蔔和歐芹根之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.83,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會讓人想起戰時的緊急糧食
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.90,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因此這些食材長時間都被人敬而遠之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:04.04,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那些想要遺忘掉的蔬菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.57,0:07:08.15,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「被遺忘的蔬菜」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,給那份洛林派命名的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.59,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫做「被遺忘的蔬菜洛林派」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:17.96,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對於接觸過法國文化還有日本文化的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.01,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一定存在著只有我才能做出來的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:21.88,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,之前你問過我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.34,0:07:25.17,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼決定這個時候來日本開店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:26.01,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:30.25,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是為了再次確認我的根本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:31.72,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「根本」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.52,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再次面對我出生的這個國家的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.30,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這對於想要奪得三星的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:40.35,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.27,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人回去酒店沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:48.74,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 別當媽媽我老人痴呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:49.99,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:51.45,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,小次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.03,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:01.29,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.04,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,新菜式比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.88,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不能錯過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能過來真是幸運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.17,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我說了快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:12.76,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到這樣的話怎麼可能回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:16.01,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,日向子的心情也是理所當然的 四宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:18.43,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為聽說幸平也參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:19.56,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想觀摩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.10,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:25.27,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,說來這還是幸平君和四宮前輩的第一次正面交鋒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:28.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,合宿時候食戟的復仇之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我聽到說什麼合宿的食戟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:37.06,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沙佩爾老師 我也不知道她在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:39.70,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,乾她可能喝醉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.66,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,紅酒喝多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.79,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,遠月的監視者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.26,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚幸平做出的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.59,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,將會成為這次實地研修的關鍵對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:54.55,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.64,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是形勢有點不太樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.18,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,正常情況下遠月的學生在初中部的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:03.44,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就已經學會了法式料理的基礎知識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.61,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他沒有這樣的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:09.28,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然在我的課上還有合宿時四宮的課題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:13.74,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他都能按照已有的法式料理配方完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:17.78,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是對於從零開始創造配方就不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.06,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且最終審查人是那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.81,0:09:24.75,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,唯也要參加比賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:25.67,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.15,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,半年前唯她還擔任著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.05,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,SHINO's總店的肉類主廚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:31.41,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:33.30,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼現在成了服務總管
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.51,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個比賽在總店那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:37.35,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,每個月都會舉行好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:40.58,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能夠採用我的料理的次數
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:42.43,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在這兩年裡就只有那麼一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:44.99,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這樣下去不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.48,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我認為成為服務總管後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:51.86,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,通過和客人直接接觸能讓我看到了更多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:55.70,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 作為廚師的鍛鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以一天都沒有鬆懈過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:58.65,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.87,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要證明出不是因為唯她被刷下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.79,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我才當上肉類主廚的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,每個人都是非常認真地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.75,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,面對這個新菜式比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.42,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而你有相當的覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:18.49,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,通過四宮前輩剛才的那番話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.60,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也看到了些曾經看不到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:25.45,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,現在腦海中只想著如何把它定型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.65,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我將會把包含覺悟在內的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:29.44,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這所有東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:32.36,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,呈現在一道菜之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:36.36,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,開始烹飪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:38.95,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1002)}oui chef
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:38.95,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 大廚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:42.40,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,首先加熱蜂蜜還有砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:43.62,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,等顏色變成糖稀色的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.47,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,加入馬丁尼和紅酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.46,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還有牛仔骨高湯進行熬煮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.08,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,同時加入牛油來煎炒雞肉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:51.50,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,使洋蔥出水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:58.26,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.28,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要那樣煎魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.64,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣煎的話魚皮就會變得更脆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:08.02,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這樣的絕招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.68,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,定食屋還真是博大精深呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:12.98,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:16.29,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,現在這樣理解也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.91,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,能告訴我嗎 創真君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:22.58,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會懂得法國料理的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:26.58,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這種煎法是我老爹教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.96,0:11:29.75,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,把魚煎得脆脆地再端出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.70,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我能清楚理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.92,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹一直以來所積累的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.54,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,把它們融會貫通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.88,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,包括所有的經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.30,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:41.52,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.80,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的感動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.97,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹他把這些都用於描繪出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:47.48,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,理想中定食屋的最強技術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.52,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在必須做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:52.69,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(966,1005)}poêler
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:52.69,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,油煎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:53.69,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(963,1008)}suer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:53.69,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,出水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:54.65,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1008)}allumette
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:54.65,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,火柴棒切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:55.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}escalope
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:55.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,帶皮薄片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:56.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1002)}déglacer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:56.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,焦糖溶化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.15,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1008)}ciselé
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:57.15,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,切絲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:57.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1026,1005)}roti
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:57.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,法式炙烤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:58.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(969,1008)}presse
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:58.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.75,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,將到目前為止的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.46,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,給打破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:38.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,至此 三人菜品的試吃就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:41.78,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,琉詩小姐 唯小姐 阿貝爾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.02,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平 最後是你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:45.37,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,菜還沒做好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.63,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:00.78,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,整整一隻鵪鶉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.09,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:06.05,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平創真 那道菜到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.72,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這道菜其實是親子蓋飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:11.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,親子蓋飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.14,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但就算這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.90,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不能算得上是蓋飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.73,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是請嚐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:21.25,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我現在能做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.07,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒的法國菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:24.66,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,鵪鶉肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.78,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在法國和意大利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:28.08,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,無論餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.41,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在家庭聚餐中也會出現的必備食材
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.29,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這在表面看來的確是一道法國菜 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:34.62,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,居然說是親子蓋飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:38.29,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,鵪鶉和水波蛋的組合所以是親子蓋飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:40.76,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你在謀劃什麼 幸平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:43.38,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我就來品嚐一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:46.39,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那一道菜裡包含了全部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:50.06,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼是否能讓四宮小次郎稱讚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:52.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,實地研修制度真正的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.52,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平是否能夠到達那個地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.15,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:13.16,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 雞蛋從裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.62,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還有燴飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.88,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.97,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,黏稠的蛋和鵪鶉肉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,並且和飯清爽地纏繞在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.85,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個口感是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.60,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,親子蓋飯的基本要素有五點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:37.27,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雞肉 蛋 飯 洋蔥 佐料汁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:41.70,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,先用油把鵪鶉肉煎過以後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.19,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再放入烤箱徹底烤熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,表面變得酥脆 肉變得鮮嫩多汁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:49.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而蛋是用鹽和黑胡椒調成辛辣味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:53.12,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然後再加入鮮奶油使其濃稠醇厚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:57.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,親子蓋飯中半熟的半熟可是生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.88,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在調味飯上輕輕掛上牛奶來煮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.21,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再加入用黃油炒的雞肉糜和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.55,0:15:06.51,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,脫水之後 香醇和甘甜都有所提升的洋蔥進行翻炒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,而醬汁則是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:11.39,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在用砂糖和蜂蜜調成微甜的馬德拉醬汁裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:12.72,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,加入醬油調成的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.73,0:15:16.65,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就用像佐料汁的東西把食材連繫起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:20.19,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 這道菜把親子蓋飯這一概念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,用法式的技巧再構建出來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:23.90,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.94,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果用調味飯那樣的東西作為鵪鶉填充料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.49,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣都應該會有液體滲出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.03,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平 你是怎麼樣填進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 剛剛的口感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.04,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是捲心菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.12,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,用鹽水焯過的捲心菜把餡包起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.90,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再填進鵪鶉體內的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:43.72,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是合宿那時候的食戟麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:48.09,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮做的法式燉捲心菜卷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.72,0:15:50.63,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煮捲心菜所用的時間控制得很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:54.47,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,即保留了清爽的口感又能突出其甘甜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:58.09,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那份甘甜把鵪鶉肉的香味和餡的配料的風味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.85,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,溫和地結合了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:04.23,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,實地研修想讓學園的學生做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:07.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是 在現場可以起到什麼作用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:10.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而真正的目的更為深遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:11.49,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,戰後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,以成為法菜專業廚師為目標的年輕廚師們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.92,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,陸續遠渡法國
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:20.04,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他們為了習藝而各路奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:24.29,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,近距離地觀摩傳說級的達人們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.42,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,學習他們的技藝 盜取 抽取出精華
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.91,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,最後 構建出了他們自己的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:34.10,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在現在的日本 真正的法國菜遍地開花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:37.73,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因為有他們嘔心瀝血的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.68,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,實地研修真正的意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:44.06,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是做曾經的年輕人做過的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是看你們能從專家那裡能夠奪取些什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.78,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真有一手啊 幸平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:55.16,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮前輩是為了提升自己法國菜的水準才回到日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:56.28,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是這樣說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:00.45,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我現在要做的事情就肯定和你相反了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.63,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為了突破在我生活的環境裡做出料理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:09.42,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我初次創作出的新的 幸平 料理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.18,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 該判定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.30,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平創真的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:18.85,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是否可以在SHINO's 的菜單上留下刻印呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.90,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 品質太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.70,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說 如果就這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:37.58,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果添在你未來所開爛店裡那也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:41.70,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果要在四宮小次郎的店鋪裡端出還欠點火候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.46,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 也算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:47.71,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我的話會如何烹飪這道菜 倒是可以教教你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.09,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:51.51,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.80,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 這種情況要用雪梨醋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.89,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,紅酒要在醋燉好以後再放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:00.56,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:03.02,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雪梨醋是西班牙產的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.52,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也別忘了撈雜質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:09.65,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 幸平創真合格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:16.48,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 讓您教我教到早上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.41,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 是你的悟性太差而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.70,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝你 四宮師父
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.87,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣 誰是你師父啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.41,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}師父
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.83,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}居然被叫師父了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.92,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,讓別人叫你師父還真是驕傲自大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.98,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煩死了 是這傢伙自己要叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.46,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是不坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.97,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明明開心得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:35.72,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:41.35,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要拿下啊 遠月十傑的第一席
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:42.31,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:44.52,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:47.59,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的實地研修會有多少學生倖存下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:52.98,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是繼合宿研修以後有大量的學生被刷掉的事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:55.86,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那些敢於直面自己極限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:58.91,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,並且還想要將之克服的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:03.83,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,才算是獲得成長這一果實的玉的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:08.21,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下一道 別停下 動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.96,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是 黑木場先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.01,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我那不良的兒子居然變得這麼老實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.14,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.26,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也給我得體一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.39,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別給其他客人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:21.90,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 黑木場先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:26.56,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,阿爾迪尼 這季的新菜開發你也來參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.91,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.61,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,僅僅是跟在哥哥後面是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.90,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,跳動跳動小鹿亂撞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:38.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,跳動跳動小鹿亂撞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:40.41,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,興奮興奮閃亮閃亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:42.71,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,興奮興奮閃亮閃亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.72,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,變得好吃起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,變得好吃起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:51.88,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請品嘗 小姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.49,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一號桌 走蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:56.01,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,八號桌 大份 淡口味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:58.22,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,九號桌 普通 半碗飯 加捲心菜和叉燒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.11,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,十一號桌 面硬點 加豆芽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.59,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,負責十二號桌的臨時工快點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:03.34,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能夠就這樣放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:05.47,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是伊武君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.93,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這家店已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.98,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請再把廚房借給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.61,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對要逆轉乾坤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:14.32,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.11,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,連招待工作也要承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你會過勞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.47,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 請讓我做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.66,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在廚房以外的地方也能發揮作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:30.12,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 如果是傳授你的話 應該再合適不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:34.79,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我所專研的開爐的奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.59,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.15,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,本想著你們兩個是龍套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.93,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但實力還真不是蓋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.35,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:47.93,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是可以讓小孩停泣的極星人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只是稍微改變了調味料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.73,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,居然就吃得這麼乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:57.61,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對 這就是香辛料的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.91,shiki Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs90\pos(966,924)\fad(400,0)}SHINO's TOKYO 正式開店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:02.07,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,主廚 我想再要一道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.45,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有沒有什麼有趣的菜品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:08.91,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我有一道可以頗具自信的菜品 可以推薦給你們品嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:13.21,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,調味飯與蛋作餡的鵪鶉 自大小鬼風味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:13.26,shokeki_huamian,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,850)}{\fs57\pos(915,324)\frz10.32\c&H636B9E&\frx350\fry356}烤製牛仔脛肉、加上鮮嫩的巨峰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:13.26,shokeki_huamian,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,850)}{\c&H636B9E&\fs57\frx352\fry0\pos(999,654)\frz11.16}調味飯與蛋作餡的鵪鶉 自大小鬼風味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:13.26,shokeki_huamian,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,850)}{\c&H636B9E&\fs57\frx346\fry358\frz10.92\move(1491,900,1509,945)}帶殼龍蝦 地中海的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.68,0:21:19.52,shiki Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(939,660)\fad(500,500)}實地研修全日程結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:20.67,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:23.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平 你是第一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:26.26,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,文緒婆婆 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.93,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 看你一那副得意的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這些 都是寄給你的 很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.81,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.23,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是食戟的申請書呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.36,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.40,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你回來了啊 幸平創真
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.97,0:21:45.32,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我是高二的甲山鐵次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:47.49,shiki Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs75\pos(477,927)}俗稱：串燒的鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:47.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我進行食戟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:52.79,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你們一年級生已經踏上了和我們高年級生同一個舞台了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:53.79,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:54.42,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:56.92,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,現在來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:54.18,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,繪里奈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:23:00.02,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 緋紗子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.21,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,食戟速報
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:07.11,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平創真？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.99,0:23:12.45,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在學園裡面盡力吸收技術和知識 進行比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:15.54,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想用自己的力量與別人碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.82,0:23:17.62,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,促進你成長的肥料的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:20.17,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可遍地都是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:23.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那在那個地方——遠月學園啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:44.40,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,招待不周
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.39,0:23:49.76,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,來圍觀的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.20,0:23:55.12,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢 會隨時隨地接受任何人的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.59,0:23:57.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你喜好地放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.76,0:23:59.42,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,別做那些麻煩的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:00.62,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,現在立馬也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:04.23,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,來幹吧 食戟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:09.51,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,招待不周
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,
